episodes.title: Investigating Ireland's connections to Epstein | The Indo Daily
episodes.description:
Irish Independent Features Writer Kim Bielenberg has thralled through the Epstein files for any connections to Ireland or Irish figures. Kim joined Tabitha Monahan on The Indo Daily to reveal what he found and the process behind it. 

Listen to this episode of The Indo Daily in full here or wherever you get your podcasts - https://www.independent.ie/podcasts/the-indo-daily/the-indo-daily-epstein-files-keir-starmer-on-the-brink-and-irish-connections-explored/a600318225.html

For more, visit https://www.independent.ie/.
